<h3>SERVICES</h3>

<div class="row">

  <div class="col s12 m6">
    <div class="card grey darken-1">
      <div class="card-content white-text">
        <span class="card-title">VEHICLE SALES</span>
        <ul class="collection">
        <li class="collection-item grey-text">We offer an extensive range of mostly one year old vehicles.    </li>
        <li class="collection-item grey-text">The majority of these cars are one owner, ex-fleet vehicles, still under manufacturer's warranty.</li>
        <li class="collection-item grey-text">In addition we stock a limited number of high quality older model cars.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card-action grey darken-3">
        <%= link_to "Vehicles for Sale", vehicles_path, class: "waves-effect waves-light btn" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <div class="col s12 m6">
    <div class="card grey darken-1">
      <div class="card-content white-text">
